以下 Dijkstra 实现使用了优先队列。该实现允许同一节点多次入队。这样做有问题吗？复杂度会变差吗？
```python
def dijkstra(graph, start):
    dist = {start: 0}
    pq = [(0, start)]  # (distance, node)
    while pq:
        d, u = heapq.heappop(pq)
        if d > dist.get(u, inf): continue  # 惰性跳过
        for v, w in graph[u]:
            new_d = d + w
            if new_d < dist.get(v, inf):
                dist[v] = new_d
                heapq.heappush(pq, (new_d, v))
    return dist
```
